<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 14:06:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>被指控在特拉维夫碾压抗议者的司机将被释放并软禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/driver-accused-of-running-over-protesters-in-tel-aviv-to-be-released-to-house-arrest/0000018e-bdbc-d871-ad9e-fffe33850000</link><description>法院表示，有合理的理由相信海姆·西洛特金犯下了这一罪行，但可能需要相当长的时间来审查他对事件的说法。警方要求推迟一天释放，以便他们可以就这一决定提出上诉</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 13:52:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/driver-accused-of-running-over-protesters-in-tel-aviv-to-be-released-to-house-arrest/0000018e-bdbc-d871-ad9e-fffe33850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方证实：真主党首次击落先进的 Hermes 900 无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-in-a-first-hezbollah-shoots-down-advanced-hermes-900-uav/0000018e-bd86-d92b-adaf-ffe63fde0000</link><description>Hermes 900 是一款多用途无人机，飞行时间为 36 小时。它的两架前身 Hermes 450 过去曾遭到袭击，但周六的拦截事件代价高昂，提醒人们以色列国防军无人机并非无懈可击</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 12:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-in-a-first-hezbollah-shoots-down-advanced-hermes-900-uav/0000018e-bd86-d92b-adaf-ffe63fde0000</guid></item><item><title>在所有施压策略都用尽的情况下，以色列和哈马斯现在必须谈判达成真正的加沙协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/all-pressure-tactics-exhausted-israel-and-hamas-must-now-negotiate-a-real-gaza-deal/0000018e-bd08-dfde-a3ef-bf7bbc180000</link><description>如果迄今为止，以色列的政策依赖于调解者的外交努力及其自身的军事力量，那么谈判现在取决于美国政府和以色列公众压力 — — 及其对总理可能构成的政治威胁</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/all-pressure-tactics-exhausted-israel-and-hamas-must-now-negotiate-a-real-gaza-deal/0000018e-bd08-dfde-a3ef-bf7bbc180000</guid></item><item><title>世界法院就指控德国在加沙战争中援助以色列的案件举行听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/world-court-opens-hearings-in-a-case-accusing-germany-of-aiding-israel-in-gaza-war/0000018e-bd28-df12-afaf-bfad44f30000</link><description>尼加拉瓜向国际法院请愿，称通过向以色列提供政治、财政和军事支持以及取消对近东救济工程处的资助，“德国正在为种族灭绝的实施提供便利”，并寻求结束德国对以色列的军事和其他援助</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 10:45:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/world-court-opens-hearings-in-a-case-accusing-germany-of-aiding-israel-in-gaza-war/0000018e-bd28-df12-afaf-bfad44f30000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：随着加沙战争进入六个月大关，内塔尼亚胡失去了议会多数席位；甘茨保持领先</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/polls-netanyahu-loses-knesset-majority-as-gaza-war-hits-six-month-mark-gantz-stays-ahead/0000018e-bd00-dbdb-adaf-bfe55e700000</link><description>两项调查均显示甘茨领导的政党以 32-30 个席位领先，内塔尼亚胡领导的利库德集团以 21-19 个席位紧随其后。两项民意调查均未显示财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇的宗教犹太复国主义跨过选举门槛</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:55:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/polls-netanyahu-loses-knesset-majority-as-gaza-war-hits-six-month-mark-gantz-stays-ahead/0000018e-bd00-dbdb-adaf-bfe55e700000</guid></item><item><title>发表以色列作家共存文章的格尔尼卡编辑辞职，称她不同意撤稿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/guernica-editor-who-published-israeli-writers-coexistence-essay-resigns/0000018e-bce5-df26-a99e-fcff51e00000</link><description>“该杂志坚持撤回该作品； 《格尔尼卡》杂志主编吉娜·摩尔 (Jina Moore) 写道：“我不这么认为。”在《格尔尼卡》撤回英裔以色列作家兼翻译家乔安娜·陈 (Joanna Chen) 的文章一个月后，她宣布辞职。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:33:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/guernica-editor-who-published-israeli-writers-coexistence-essay-resigns/0000018e-bce5-df26-a99e-fcff51e00000</guid></item><item><title>亲爱的拜登总统，您同意以色列定居者使用美国武器吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/fyi-joe-biden-israels-settlers-use-american-weapons/0000018e-b82b-d906-a5cf-babfb7800000</link><description>这些武器正被一个与军队类似的恐吓、恐怖和掠夺政权所使用，该政权是由国家公民及其代理人在西岸建立的政权</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/fyi-joe-biden-israels-settlers-use-american-weapons/0000018e-b82b-d906-a5cf-babfb7800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列电视台会遭遇与俄罗斯电视台同样的命运吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/will-israeli-television-suffer-the-same-fate-as-russia/0000018e-b8b6-db6c-a9ee-fcb6ace40000</link><description>在系列狂热历史上，这是第一次没有以色列节目参加今年的主要节日 - 考虑到加沙战争的状况，以色列制作人不应感到惊讶。这并不意味着以色列在边缘地区没有强大的存在</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 07:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/will-israeli-television-suffer-the-same-fate-as-russia/0000018e-b8b6-db6c-a9ee-fcb6ace40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队从加沙南部撤军，但没有实现其主要目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/one-step-away-from-victory-as-israels-soldiers-march-out-of-southern-gaza-really/0000018e-b9ef-df26-a99e-f9ffd03f0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理所追求的胜利并不像他所描述的那么接近：以色列国防军士兵正在离开加沙南部，以色列离实现战争目标并不远，现在必须应对西方更多的反对</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 03:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article/.premium/one-step-away-from-victory-as-israels-soldiers-march-out-of-southern-gaza-really/0000018e-b9ef-df26-a99e-f9ffd03f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长：我们正处于释放加沙人质的正确时机，“我们将承担代价”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article-live/report-israel-hamas-making-progress-toward-hostage-deal-after-cairo-negotiations/0000018e-bb73-df26-a99e-fb7f5b100000</link><description>外国外交官表示，埃及关于加沙谈判进展的报道中存在“谨慎乐观” ■ 哈马斯否认谈判取得进展，称以色列“拒绝了所有要求” ■ 以色列国防军称，真主党精锐拉德万部队高级指挥官被杀 ■ 约旦河西岸疑似发生恐怖袭击事件</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 02:54:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-08/ty-article-live/report-israel-hamas-making-progress-toward-hostage-deal-after-cairo-negotiations/0000018e-bb73-df26-a99e-fb7f5b100000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击事件已过去六个月，数千人集会要求人质返回</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/thousands-rally-for-hostages-return-on-six-month-mark-of-oct-7-hamas-attack/0000018e-b9e5-d712-a3df-f9ef96970000</link><description>该活动由人质和失踪家庭论坛组织，该论坛解释说，在耶路撒冷举行集会源于希望靠近决策地点，旨在提高不住在特拉维夫的以色列人的认识</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 20:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/thousands-rally-for-hostages-return-on-six-month-mark-of-oct-7-hamas-attack/0000018e-b9e5-d712-a3df-f9ef96970000</guid></item><item><title>美国预计将提出新的人质交易提案；以色列官员不确定哈马斯会放松立场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-to-propose-new-hostage-deal-israeli-officials-unsure-hamas-will-ease-position/0000018e-b9f9-d7ee-a39e-fdff2d210000</link><description>美国政府正在利用其影响力向哈马斯和以色列施加压力，因为双方在谈判中的红线问题上仍存在争执。以色列代表团周日一直在开罗进行会谈</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 20:39:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-to-propose-new-hostage-deal-israeli-officials-unsure-hamas-will-ease-position/0000018e-b9f9-d7ee-a39e-fdff2d210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军官员：汗尤尼斯撤军是行动需要，不是人质交易的姿态</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/idf-officials-khan-yunis-withdrawal-is-operational-need-not-gesture-for-hostage-deal/0000018e-b9f1-df26-a99e-f9ffa5800000</link><description>以色列军队早就明白，让军队驻扎在加沙会给他们带来危险，并希望他们的缺席会导致“另一方从其藏身之处现身”——即使面临以色列再次遭受火箭弹袭击的风险</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 20:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/idf-officials-khan-yunis-withdrawal-is-operational-need-not-gesture-for-hostage-deal/0000018e-b9f1-df26-a99e-f9ffa5800000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列服役时间最长的巴勒斯坦安全囚犯死于癌症</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/longest-serving-palestinian-security-prisoner-in-israel-dies-from-cancer/0000018e-b9c9-df26-a99e-f9ffc1350000</link><description>瓦利德·达卡 (Walid Daka) 曾参与 1984 年杀害一名以色列国防军士兵的行动，自从被诊断出患有癌症后的两年内，他多次申请提前释放，但均遭到拒绝。他在以色列监狱服刑近40年，去世享年62岁</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 19:10:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/longest-serving-palestinian-security-prisoner-in-israel-dies-from-cancer/0000018e-b9c9-df26-a99e-f9ffc1350000</guid></item><item><title>麦当劳决定回购以色列餐厅的背后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/mcdonalds-israel-buyback-caving-to-boycott-or-business-sense/0000018e-b963-d712-a3df-f9eb591a0000</link><description>该连锁店表示，此举是其频繁洗牌加盟商的一部分，但批评人士表示，由于穆斯林世界的销售低迷，该公司向 BDS 抗议者让步了</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 17:40:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/mcdonalds-israel-buyback-caving-to-boycott-or-business-sense/0000018e-b963-d712-a3df-f9eb591a0000</guid></item><item><title>至少水獭正在返回以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/at-least-the-otters-are-returning-to-israels-north/0000018e-b985-db6c-a9ee-fd95a6980000</link><description>由于水资源减少和致命的道路交叉口而几乎灭绝后，对水獭粪便的调查显示，在高速公路下为它们建造的安全通道的帮助下，它们已经回到了以色列北部失踪的地区</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 17:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/nature-environment/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/at-least-the-otters-are-returning-to-israels-north/0000018e-b985-db6c-a9ee-fd95a6980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府表示不会弥合与总检察长在极端正统派军队征兵豁免问题上的分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-says-no-bridging-gaps-with-ag-on-ultra-orthodox-army-exemption/0000018e-b92c-d8b4-a3be-fd2f473c0000</link><description>在总检察长告诉以色列高等法院，没有法律依据可以免除极端正统派人士服兵役后，政府提出了独立代表的请求。上周，一项冻结犹太学校预算的命令开始生效，学生们避免入伍</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 17:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-says-no-bridging-gaps-with-ag-on-ultra-orthodox-army-exemption/0000018e-b92c-d8b4-a3be-fd2f473c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡谈到“全面胜利”。那么，以色列国防军为何要从加沙南部撤军呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-07/ty-article/.highlight/why-is-the-idf-withdrawing-from-southern-gaza/0000018e-b945-d712-a3df-f9ef58750000</link><description>哈马斯袭击以色列六个月后，以色列国防军将从加沙南部撤军，但内塔尼亚胡并不急于结束战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:55:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-07/ty-article/.highlight/why-is-the-idf-withdrawing-from-southern-gaza/0000018e-b945-d712-a3df-f9ef58750000</guid></item><item><title>以色列右翼抗议者大肆宣扬阴谋，度过了一个疯狂的夜晚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/a-wild-night-with-israels-conspiracy-spouting-right-wing-protesters/0000018e-b930-df26-a99e-f97fccf30000</link><description>如果以色列司法部长官邸附近的一小群示威者可信的话，那么 BDS 运动是耶路撒冷反内塔尼亚胡抗议活动的资助者之一，而且“对伤害右翼政客的人的制裁还不够” &amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/a-wild-night-with-israels-conspiracy-spouting-right-wing-protesters/0000018e-b930-df26-a99e-f97fccf30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 184 天：英国首相卡梅伦表示英国对以色列的支持并非无条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-184-u-k-support-for-israel-not-unconditional-fm-cameron-says/0000018e-b967-d8b4-a3be-fd6f1aca0001</link><description>以色列国防军从加沙南部撤军 ■ 伊朗高级官员：以色列大使馆都不安全 ■ 以色列国防机构已“完成伊朗应对所需的准备” ■ 以色列代表团前往开罗进行人质释放/停火协议谈判 ■ 英国支持外交大臣卡梅伦称以色列“并非无条件” ■ 约旦河西岸枪击事件造成三人受伤 ■ 战争结束 184 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:38:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-184-u-k-support-for-israel-not-unconditional-fm-cameron-says/0000018e-b967-d8b4-a3be-fd6f1aca0001</guid></item></channel></rss>